.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, nectarine, pineapple, potato
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, superhero, horror, drama
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
4. the person eating potato is not to the right of the person watching horror movies##8
5. the person eating peach is the person watching musical movies##1
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the person eating potato##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Food   | pineapple   | nectarine         | potato   | peach    |
| Movie-Genre         | superhero | drama | horror | musical |

