.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, march, october, september
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, alhambra, siglo, prince
1. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in march##7
2. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5
3. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in april##7
4. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the prince-smoker##8
5. the prince-smoker is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the alhambra-smoker##7
6. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
7. the alhambra-smoker is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
8. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | march   | october | september | april    |
| Cigar         | dunhill | prince   | siglo   | alhambra |

