.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, freelancer, scientist, project-manager
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, grey, chestnut, emerald
1. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
3. the scientist is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
5. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the freelancer##5
6. the project-manager is not to the left of the person who likes grey##8
7. the project-manager is the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Job          | project-manager | librarian | freelancer  | scientist |
| Color   | grey   | emerald         | chestnut | blood-red |

