The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, indie, hip-hop, jazz
1. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the fan of jazz##8
2. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
3. the person playing domino is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere between the fan of indie and the person playing domino##7
5. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8
6. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the fan of indie and the person playing backgammon##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Game     | domino | backgammon | monopoly | whist     |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | hip-hop        | jazz          | indie |

