.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, sprite, lemonade
City: paris, colone, nizza, marseilles
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking lemonade and the person traveling to paris##2
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to paris##5
5. the person traveling to colone is the person traveling to colone##1
6. the person drinking sprite is not the person traveling to nizza##6
7. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
8. the person traveling to paris is not to the left of the person traveling to colone##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | fanta | sprite | cola |
| City     | marseilles | colone       | paris  | nizza    |

