2. the british is not the person traveling to hannover##6
3. the british is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
5. the british is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
6. the brazilian is not to the right of the british##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| City         | san-francisco | edinburgh      | miami   | hannover  |
| Nationality   | australian    | brazilian | british | thai |

