3. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
4. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the pakistani is between the pall-mall-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##2
6. the turkish is on the far left##1
7. the pakistani is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality    | turkish        | argentine | pakistani      | colombian    |
| Cigar   | bolivar | ritmeester   | old-henry | pall-mall |

