.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, lily, daffodil, dahlia
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, february, may, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8
2. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##8
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who growslily##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who growslily##7
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
8. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Flower   | dahlia | lily         | daffodil    | balloon-flower       |
| Birthday      | february | october | july | may |

