.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
House: farmhouse, futuristic, modern, cape-cod
4 different games are played: whist, monopoly, poker, canasta
 1. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
 2. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the modern house##8
 3. the farmhouse house is the person playing poker##1
 4. the person playing poker is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8
 5. the person playing canasta is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 6. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the farmhouse house is not to the right of the person playing poker##8
 9. the person playing monopoly is not to the left of the farmhouse house##8
10. the futuristic house is not to the left of the person playing whist##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| House          | futuristic    | modern | farmhouse | cape-cod |
| Game   | whist | canasta  | poker     | monopoly    |

