.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, traveling, gardening, card-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, rugby, lacrosse, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
2. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
8. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby           | gardening | card-games | traveling | filmmaking   |
| Sport   | lacrosse       | weightlifting      | rugby    | swimming |

