5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport    | volleyball        | water-polo | rugby | snowboarding |
| Flower   | tulip | zinnia | begonia   | rose    |

