.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, traveling, cooking, collecting
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, librarian, videographer, coach
1. the librarian is not the person who's hobby is chess##6
2. the videographer is on the right of the coach##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the coach##8
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is the dancer##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the librarian and the dancer##7
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
7. the videographer is between the coach and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling    | collecting | chess | cooking |
| Job   | librarian | coach      | videographer     | dancer     |

 